death song ( hangul : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; hanja : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ; rr : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 1991 south korean film directed by kim &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . it won multiple awards in the 1991 chunsa film art awards , including best film , the 1991 blue dragon film awards , again including best film , and the 1992 grand bell awards .